"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-olympics-2024-burgess-team-gb-b1173661.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  Adam Burgessbanished the sleepless nights of Tokyo asTeam GB's slalom canoeists continued their superb start to2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 290, \"end\": 295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9995801662974148, \"rank\": 0.00041190281596739355, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 305, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.8530013343029541, \"rank\": 0.1718833164326029, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burgessclaimed a stunning silver in the men's single, three years after missing out on a medal by an agonising margin of just 0.16seconds.\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 510, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There'll be no waking up in the night, wondering what could have been now,\\\" said the 32-year-old.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really wanted to just leave it all out there today.\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have paid the price and missed opportunities by being a little cautious at times.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I really wanted to just go out with confidence.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 803, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot of people were saying I had to be lucky and I was maybe not the one that was talked about for winning a medal.\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 922, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That gave me a bit of more grit to go and prove people wrong today.\\\"\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Burgess was just outside the medal places in qualifying, having been fourth-fastest in the afternoon's semi-finals, but produced a superb run when it mattered to finish runner-up behind home favourite Nicolas Gestin.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1194, \"end\": 1208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Gestin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nicolas Gestin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Gestin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicolas_Gestin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table: Latest count today after Team GB rush on day three  Afterwards, he revealed being inspired by teammate Kimberley Woods, who had been only 12th-fastest in the women's heats on the opening day of the Games before upping her game in the semis and final to grab bronze.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1503, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999999436113, \"rank\": 5.5911953615427055e-11, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Woods\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kimberley Woods\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Woods\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Woods\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was thinking about Kimberley, who made a similar error yesterday and charged up and got herself on to the podium,\\\" he added. \\\"\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Walsh\", \"score\": 0.9999954186974159, \"rank\": 2.293040997811614e-06, \"text\": \"Kimberley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Walsh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kimberley_Walsh\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was trying to harness a bit of that grit and determination and finish the run-off strong.\\\"\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal X